Package jwiki.util

Classes with static methods that support the jwiki core framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FError
    Error handling methods.
    FL
    Static Collections and Stream utilities.
    FString
    Frequently used, static String functions.
    GroupQueue<T>
    A simple read-only Queue that allows multiple items to be polled at once.
    JSONP
    Static JSON-parsing methods
    MapList<K,V>
    A HashMap which allows multiple values for each key.
    Tuple<K,V>
    Simple implementation of a Tuple.

Package jwiki.util Description

Classes with static methods that support the jwiki core framework. These are very general, and may be helpful in applications that build on jwiki.
Author:
Fastily
